Kara Tointon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kara_Tointon 0 Kara Louise Tointon (born 5 August 1983) is an English actress, best known for playing Dawn Swann in BBC soap opera EastEnders, as the 2010 winner of BBC television series Strictly Come Dancing and as Maria in the ITV live production of The Sound of Music Live in December 2015 alongside Julian Ovenden as Captain von Trapp. Kara_Louise_Tointon ( born_5_August_1983 ) is an_English_actress , best_known for playing Dawn_Swann in BBC_soap_opera_EastEnders , as the_2010_winner of BBC_television_series Strictly Come Dancing and as Maria in the_ITV_live_production of The_Sound of Music_Live in December_2015 alongside Julian_Ovenden as Captain_von_Trapp .
